<html lang='en'>
  <head>
    <meta charset='UTF-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>WMC Intranet Account Activation Link</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .content {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>Hello there, {{name}}!</div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>You are one step closer to activating your account in the WMC
          Intranet Portal. Make sure to double check the details before
          activating your account.</p>
        <p>Double check your personal
          <a href='http://localhost:3000//register?id={{id}}'>here</a>
          to fully activate your account</p>
        <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reply to this email, we will
          be happy to assist you.</p>

        <p>Best regards,<br /> IT</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply directly to this
          email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>